    "quite a fine name you bestowed.\p"
    "But! What say you, if I were to\n"
    "suggest a slightly better name?")
}

text SlateportCity_NameRatersHouse_Text_WhatShallNewNameBe {
   format("Ah, good. Then, what shall the new\n"
